\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi720\li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \i\fs24\lang3082\langfe3082\cgrid\langnp3082\langfenp3082 {En el transcurso de aquellos d\'ed
